snippet.title: AMBER HEARD ON THE STAND! ATTEMPTS TO PORTRAY HERSELF AS A SAINT🙄 Depp vs Heard Trial HER TESTIMONY
snippet.description:
On day 14 of the Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard (Depp vs Heard) defamation lawsuit trial, Amber Heard is on the stand, testifying and makes a weak attempt to portray herself in a saintly light, as she expresses to the jury that she was a volunteer for deaf children and would kick random 12 year old's out of classrooms. Is Amber Heard lying in court? Or did she really kick 12 year old's out of classrooms? I think she's actually being honest about this one😂 If anything, it makes the list for the Depp vs Heard trial funny moments...

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #DeppvsHeard
